        "title": "Add Mistral balance metrics",
        "body": "## Summary\r\n- Add Mistral credit-balance fetching from the authenticated Mistral billing web session.\r\n- Show Mistral balance in the provider card using the same compact balance treatment as DeepSeek.\r\n- Preserve existing Mistral menu-bar behavior: Pay-as-you-go shows API spend, while Monthly Plan shows Vibe subscription usage.\r\n- Avoid falling back to API spend when Monthly Plan data is unavailable, so the menu-bar picker stays honest.\r\n- Add Mistral visual meter support in the menu-bar icon and provider switcher, so the colored bars reflect the selected Mistral metric instead of only showing text.\r\n- Update README, provider docs, and Settings copy to describe API spend, credit balance, and Monthly Plan usage accurately.\r\n\r\n## Why\r\nMistral exposes different billing views for API spend, credit balance, and optional Monthly Plan usage. CodexBar already showed spend/monthly-plan data, but not the available credit balance, which made pay-as-you-go accounts harder to inspect.\r\n\r\n## Validation\r\n- `swift test --filter ProvidersPaneCoverageTests`\r\n- `plutil -lint Sources/CodexBar/Resources/en.lproj/Localizable.strings`\r\n- `git diff --check`\r\n- `make check`\r\n\r\n## Screenshot\r\n###  menu\r\nbefore\r\n<img width=\"308\" height=\"191\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-06-28 at 15 36 27\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c6302bd7-1181-41aa-b893-571a1b1870eb\" />\r\n\r\nafter\r\n<img width=\"309\" height=\"236\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-06-28 at 14 05 32\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/72693c00-7e03-47b2-bed5-11335d03603f\" />\r\n\r\n###  menu-bar icon and provider switcher\r\nbefore \r\n<img width=\"306\" height=\"118\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-06-28 at 15 36 44\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/8655abfd-7eb7-47a4-a78b-5e22a2c4a1eb\" />\r\n\r\nafter\r\n<img width=\"312\" height=\"119\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-06-28 at 14 45 27\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/8a4a78b7-5728-47d5